@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - KhumaloCraft Emporium</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/style.css" />
    <style>
        .about-section {
            padding: 50px 0; /* top and bottom padding of 50px, left and right padding of 0 */
        }

        .about-content {
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .logo-banner {
            background-image: url('/Images/KhumaloCraftsBanner.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 400px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container">
        <section class="about-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4" style="margin-left: -15px;">
                    <!-- Add negative left margin -->
                    <div class="logo-banner"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h2>KhumaloCraft Emporium</h2>
                        <h3>Our Story</h3>
                        <p>KhumaloCraft Emporium was created through the vision of James Khumalo, a passionate entrepreneur dedicated to showcasing handcrafted products from artisans around the world. We believe in connecting these skilled creators with a broad audience who can really appreciate the beauty and uniqueness of handcrafted pieces.</p>

                        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                        <p><strong>Champion Artisanship:</strong> We honor the artistry and dedication that it takes to create beautiful and unique pieces and offer artisans a space to share their stories and connect with customers.</p>
                        <p><strong>Connecting Creators &amp; Collectors:</strong> We close the gap between talented artisans and tasteful customers that seek out to find only the best handcrafted pieces.</p>
                        <p><strong>Creating a Global Marketplace:</strong> We eliminate all geographical boundaries, curating a global marketplace where artisans can reach a broad audience and customers can acquire hidden gems from all around the world.</p>

                        <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
                        <p>We are committed to building a:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Scalable Platform: Our platform is created to accommodate exponential growth, ensuring the best experience for artisans and customers.</li>
                            <li>Accessible For Everyone: One of our main priorities is global access, allowing artisans from anywhere to show off their work to customers from all across the globe.</li>
                            <li>Secure Environment: Security is of utmost importance, we promise to keep customer information and artisan data safe from threats.</li>
                            <li>Positive User Experience: Most importantly, we want to make the platform user-friendly and strive to seamlessly integrate the buying and selling process, allowing only smiles on the faces of everyone that visits our website.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3>The Future of KhumaloCraft</h3>
                        <p>Just as the artists are innovators, we too will strive for constant innovation to only better user experience while continuing to add advanced features like:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Powerful Search Capabilities</li>
                            <li>Personalized Notifications</li>
                            <li>Streamlined Processes</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>By creating a platform that is driven by artistry and made with the newest technology, KhumaloCraft Emporium is taking all the steps to become the leading global platform for handcrafted products through empowering artisans and enhancing the lives of its customers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>